  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve]Lv.6 w/[Imperialdramon]\_in its name: Cost 5
    \n\n[Hand] [Counter] \uFF1CBlast Digivolve\uFF1E \n[On Play] [When Digivolving]
